{"tid":41440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉劉淑儀：回港多年來的經歷是「臥薪嘗膽」","createTime":"2016-12-16T01:55:21.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T11:22:32.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f40d270214f2e7eeb0132dfa060d7b91d2d8b53f","tid":41440,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T01:55:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D9m8miq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD9m8miq.jpg&h=1d30c57b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正式宣布參選行政長官的新民黨主席葉劉淑儀在電台節目表示，重啟政改及基本法23條立法的問題難度同樣高，認為應一同處理。但她強調，首要應該解決房屋問題。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀的政綱提到下屆政府應讓「忠誠的反對派」參與管治，她舉例指民主思路召集人湯家驊是忠誠反對派，因為對方不會當釋法是洪水猛獸。<br />\n<br />\n她形容多年來的經歷是「臥薪嘗膽」，從外國回港參選時看盡人情冷暖，感覺辛酸。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1302676-20161216.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1302676-20161216.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Ng4LGNcEoVVedGM5ARmsm0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=38450239\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1302676-20161216.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=1b13fe4d\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1302676-20161216.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"2624b553fea71e301ac746e47912535aeee0b1a5","tid":41440,"uid":4324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T01:56:13.000Z","msg":"湯渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"436b099a0e1d8ac0adb13e3faa5ea6688fc41163","tid":41440,"uid":9069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T01:56:28.000Z","msg":"食屎啦"},{"pid":"84441e7ce4973c4e11678269f8f7647e6fae46ec","tid":41440,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T01:56:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7047bdcef9126e3790263fda9ac5318d88e2ed1a","tid":41